SELECT u.username, COUNT(p.preference_id) AS num_preferences FROM users u LEFT JOIN preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id GROUP BY u.username;
SELECT u.username, AVG(p.notifications_enabled::int) AS avg_notifications_enabled FROM users u LEFT JOIN preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id GROUP BY u.username;
SELECT u.username, MAX(p.notifications_enabled::int) AS max_notifications_enabled FROM users u LEFT JOIN preferences p ON u.user_id = p.user_id GROUP BY u.username;

SELECT username, SUM(CASE WHEN notifications_enabled THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_enabled_notifications FROM preferences GROUP BY username;
SELECT username, ARRAY_AGG(theme) AS themes FROM preferences GROUP BY username;
SELECT username, STRING_AGG(theme, ',') AS all_themes FROM preferences GROUP BY username;
SELECT username, STRING_AGG(theme, ',') AS distinct_themes FROM (SELECT DISTINCT username, theme FROM preferences) t GROUP BY username;
SELECT username, STRING_AGG(CONCAT(theme, ' (', language, ')'), ', ') AS theme_language_combos FROM preferences GROUP BY username;

SELECT u.username, p.language, COUNT(p.user_id) AS total_preferences FROM users AS u JOIN preferences AS p ON u.user_id = p.user_id GROUP BY u.username, p.language HAVING COUNT(p.user_id) > 1;

SELECT u.username, COUNT(p.preference_id) AS total_preferences FROM users AS u JOIN preferences AS p ON u.user_id = p.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING COUNT(p.preference_id) > 2 ORDER BY total_preferences DESC;

SELECT u.username, COALESCE(p.theme, 'light') AS user_theme FROM users AS u LEFT JOIN preferences AS p ON u.user_id = p.user_id;
